--- .gitignore (原始)
```
# Compiled and build artifacts
*.pyc
__pycache__/
*.o
*.obj
dist/
build/
target/

# Dependencies
.venv/
venv/
node_modules/
.mypy_cache/
.pytest_cache/
.coverage

# Logs and temp files
*.log
*.tmp
*.swp
*.swo

# Environment
.env
.env.local
.env.*

# Editors
.vscode/
.idea/

# System files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Coverage
coverage/
htmlcov/

# Gradle
.gradle/

# Compressed files
*.zip
*.gz
*.tar
*.tgz
*.bz2
*.xz
*.7z
*.rar
*.zst
*.lz4
*.lzh
*.cab
*.arj
*.rpm
*.deb
*.Z
*.lz
*.lzo
*.tar.gz
*.tar.bz2
*.tar.xz
*.tar.zst
```

+++ .gitignore (修改后)
Nothing needs to be added to .gitignore since the changes only include source code files (.js and .php) without any build artifacts, dependencies, or temporary files.